  or word, you can do so <%= link_to "here", 
	                           problems_path, 
														 class: 'accentLink' %>. 
  You can refine your search by filtering problems with proofs or ones 
	that don't have any yet. You can also sort based on date created or 
	modified, problems with most upvotes or problems with most proofs.
</p>

